			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify;  background-color: #000016;   background-image: none;  background-repeat: repeat-x; " >
												<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>Based on the response to the other thread I think there's quite a few people with opinions on what should, and shouldn't be changed in PvP.&nbsp; So here's the place to post your list of things for us to change to make the EverQuest PvP world a better place.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I'll warn you up front, there's going to be heavy moderation on this thread for anything that doesn't directly relate to the question above, so please keep it on topic.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I'll even start it off with my list:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>- Resist System imbalances at high levels</DIV>
<DIV>- Lack of real rewards for PvP combat</DIV>
<DIV>- Safe zones rendering most locations impractical for PvP</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>There's other more specific problems as well, but in my mind those are the major ones.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>If you agree, or disagree I want to know.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>-Ryan</DIV>
																		
