			<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; " >
												<P>I think it's too late to save PvP in EQ, especially since what makes a character powerful in EQ are items, the very things that unbalance the game.&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>
<P>Why don't you guys cap resist ??&nbsp; Say resist capped at 150 (just and example)or so would solve some of the problems with people inmune to spells.</P>
<P>Make it so HT, LoH, and such abilities are not refreshed upon death. </P>
<P>Make fear and charm work again.&nbsp; That would give the non-evils a fighting chance. </P>
<P>Training it's not fun. Even on SZ. Lets be real, the no rules server except when it came to Fansy the bard. </P>
<P>Hell. Lets kick it up a notch. Remove the damage cap from nukes (base the damage on resists)&nbsp;and ungimp pets.&nbsp; Make like it was before, fire pets had high fire resists , necro pets could have high disease resist. Take away the "pet has the master's resists nonsense"</P>
<P>But always remember. The problems that affect the blue servers magnify exponentially in PvP. </P>
