												<DIV>I am not sure what all needs to be fixed, PvP in my opinion has been so messed up in EverQuest that the only way to fix it would be to make a new game. But I do believe that no class should have it's class ability taken away in pvp ( Lay on Hands and Harm Touch) specifically . The Damage down to 66% of spells and abilities like these have already been done.&nbsp; Also, I know HT and LoH dont come back after the Shadow Knight or Paladin die. It still takes &nbsp;about 1 hour and 12 minutes for the ability to come back unless they have AA to lower that time. </FONT></DIV>
