<DIV>As far as resistances go, I dont think that they should be nerfed into a pvp mode like some have suggested (if you worked hard to get good gear only for your resistances to be nerfed in pvp you wouldnt be happy).</FONT></DIV>
<DIV></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
